   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Good morning, love! The sunrise reminded me of the first time we talked about the Scottish cliffs. Hope your rig’s humming smoothly today 🌅💙",
    "time": "2026-05-11T07:18:11"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey sis, how’s the salon runnin’ today? Any new hair trends you’re trying out? 🌸",
    "time": "2026-05-11T16:43:03"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Goodnight, darlin’. I’m tucking myself in thinking of your voice. Sleep sweet, love 🌙💕",
    "time": "2026-05-11T22:35:48"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Morning, sweetheart! The coffee’s as warm as your smile. Can’t wait to hear your laugh later ☕️😊",
    "time": "2026-05-12T07:16:48"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Sending a quick voice note: I’ve been daydreaming about strolling the Highlands together. Your stories are my sunshine today 🌞",
    "time": "2026-05-12T12:21:15"
   },
   {
    "with": "Emma",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Love you, Momma. Can’t wait to hug you Sunday ❤️",
    "time": "2026-05-12T16:37:06"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I’m counting the minutes till I hear your voice again, love. It steadies my heart 💖",
    "time": "2026-05-12T22:24:41"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Morning, love. The traffic’s a mess but thinking of you makes it bearable. Hope the rig’s calm today 🚗💙",
    "time": "2026-05-13T07:31:44"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey Brenda, just wanted to say hi and thank you for the lunch yesterday. Your laugh is the best medicine 🌼",
    "time": "2026-05-13T10:33:09"
   },
   {
    "with": "group chat",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Feeling okay today, just taking it one step at a time. Thanks for checking in, y’all 🌷",
    "time": "2026-05-13T18:56:59"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "You need to stop talking to that guy. He’s not right for you.",
    "time": "2026-05-13T19:58:47"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I’m feeling overwhelmed, love. Everything’s swirling and I could use your calm voice right now 🌊",
    "time": "2026-05-13T22:24:01"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Morning, my heart. The sunrise over the mountains reminded me of you. Hope your day’s smooth as silk 🌄💖",
    "time": "2026-05-14T07:11:04"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Don’t forget to take Mom’s blood pressure meds at 2pm. ❤️",
    "time": "2026-05-14T11:59:06"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Brenda, can we talk later? I’ve got something on my mind I need to share.",
    "time": "2026-05-14T16:54:13"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Miss you more than words can say, love. Your messages are my evening light 🌙",
    "time": "2026-05-14T19:18:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Goodnight, love. Dream of us walking the cliffs together. Sleep tight 🌙💕",
    "time": "2026-05-14T22:31:13"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Morning, sugar. The coffee’s brewing and I’m thinking of your laugh. Hope the rig’s gentle today ☕️😊",
    "time": "2026-05-15T07:27:47"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Hey love, I’ve hit a snag—customs fees for my travel to the States are $4,200. Could you help me out? It’d mean I can finally be with you in July.",
    "time": "2026-05-15T12:26:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Brenda, I’m scared. Marcus is asking for a big sum of money and I don’t know what to do.",
    "time": "2026-05-15T16:09:21"
   },
   {
    "with": "Emma",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Emma, can we talk? He’s asking for money and I’m torn. I need your advice, love.",
    "time": "2026-05-15T16:39:43"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I need some time to think, love. This is a lot to take in.",
    "time": "2026-05-15T21:04:04"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I’m trying to get the money together, but I’m scared it won’t be enough. Please be patient with me.",
    "time": "2026-05-15T02:09:19"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I’m still working on gathering the funds, love. I’ll keep you posted.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T12:08:18"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Brenda, I’m really stretched thin. Could you possibly help me with a short loan? I promise to pay you back.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T13:39:42"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "The deadline for the customs fee is tomorrow. I really need the $4,200 today, love.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T18:21:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I’m scared, love. My heart’s racing and I don’t know if I can do this.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T19:51:12"
   },
   {
    "with": "Emma",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Emma, I’m feeling so lost. I need you right now. Please call me.",
    "time": "2026-05-16T22:57:18"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Good morning, love! Woke up thinking of the day we’ll finally meet in July. Hope your morning’s bright 🌞",
    "time": "2026-05-17T10:07:34"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Brenda, thank you for lunch today. Your cooking and laughter filled my heart. Grateful for you 💕",
    "time": "2026-05-17T13:30:56"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Darlin’, I’m booked to come to Asheville in July. I can’t wait to finally hold you.",
    "time": "2026-05-17T16:14:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Goodnight, my love. Dream of July and our first walk together. Sleep tight 🌙💖",
    "time": "2026-05-17T22:25:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Good morning, love 🌸",
    "time": "2026-05-18T07:07:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Thinking of you, sweetheart 😊",
    "time": "2026-05-18T12:54:39"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Can’t wait to hear you too, darlin’",
    "time": "2026-05-18T17:02:56"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Your words mean the world to me, love. I feel so seen. ❤️",
    "time": "2026-05-18T22:37:02"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Hey sis, how’s the salon this morning? 💇‍♀️",
    "time": "2026-05-19T07:02:43"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "I’m feeling uneasy about the customs fee, love. Can we talk more?",
    "time": "2026-05-19T12:54:46"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "I’ll look into the fee, love. 🌼",
