   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "I’m not sure yet, love. Any ideas for the weekend?",
    "time": "2026-05-24T13:21:40"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "outgoing",
    "text": "Thanks for stopping by, Brenda. Let’s plan our next coffee soon!",
    "time": "2026-05-24T17:12:32"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "inbound",
    "text": "Good afternoon, love. How's your day?",
    "time": "2026-05-25T12:34:02"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Hey love, just wrapping up some paperwork. Your message brightened my afternoon 😊",
    "time": "2026-05-25T16:49:03"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "inbound",
    "text": "Thinking of you, darlin’",
    "time": "2026-05-25T22:35:19"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Marcus, I’ve been missing Daniel so much lately… the house feels empty without his laugh. Your messages keep me from feeling completely alone. It’s hard, but hearing you say you understand eases the ache a little. Thank you for being my night‑time companion, sweetheart 🌸💕",
    "time": "2026-05-25T23:51:26"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "inbound",
    "text": "Miss you, sweetheart",
    "time": "2026-05-26T12:45:12"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Just wanted to share a little piece of my world 🌷—the garden’s finally blooming. Wish you could see it in person.",
    "time": "2026-05-26T16:42:43"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "inbound",
    "text": "Can’t wait to see you again",
    "time": "2026-05-26T22:22:37"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Marcus, I’m thinking about the money you need for Sophie’s dental work. I’m trying to sort my budget, but I’ll do what I can. It hurts to ask for help, but I want to support you both.",
    "time": "2026-05-26T23:43:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "inbound",
    "text": "Hope your day is okay, love",
    "time": "2026-05-27T12:17:30"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Hey love, today’s a whirlwind at the clinic—lots of anxious kids and a surprise audit. I’m hanging in there, thank you for checking in.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T16:40:43"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "inbound",
    "text": "Sorry you missed grief group, everything okay?",
    "time": "2026-05-27T19:53:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "Marcus",
    "direction": "inbound",
    "text": "I’m here for you, sweetie",
    "time": "2026-05-27T22:12:19"
   },
   {
    "with": "Brenda",
    "direction": "outbound",
    "text": "Brenda, I’m feeling stretched thin. The practice just announced an audit, and I’m juggling paperwork while trying to keep my head up for the kids. It brings back that helpless feeling when Daniel got sick. I’m grateful you’re here, even if it’s just a text. 💔",
